data.description: Welcome to this charming 1-story home nestled in a well-established neighborhood. With four bedrooms and two bathrooms, this spacious abode offers plenty of room. The all-brick exterior exudes timeless appeal, while the covered patio and oversized yard with a pool provide the perfect setting for outdoor gatherings and beating the summer heat. The icing on the cake? No back neighbor! Inside, you'll find a large living area with cathedral ceilings, a separate dining/breakfast area, and two rooms with direct access to the pool. Located near major highways, restaurants, groceries, and churches, convenience is at your fingertips. Although some TLC is needed, the home has never flooded. Don't miss out - schedule your tour today!
